# Normalize all text files to LF in the repository and check them out with LF,
# regardless of core.autocrlf. This kills the phantom whole-file "modified" diffs
# git was reporting on IDE-saved files (src/analyzer.ts, analyzer.html) that were
# byte-identical to HEAD. Binary assets are excluded so git never normalizes them.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.png binary
